<lyrics>[V1]
.Dm             C          Bb
 Hayot yoĘ»li va soĘ»zlaring koĘ»rsat bizga
.C           Bb           Am
 Mashaqqatli olov yoĘ»ldan oĘ»tkaz bizni
.Dm            C             Bb
 Men yolvorib agar chaqirsam eshit meni
.C         Bb             Am       Dm
 Yuragimda muqaddas Ruh ulugĘ»lab Seni!

[C1]
   Iymon qayigĘ»in tebratadi toshqin daryo
   Chu toĘ»fonda ham kaloming sochar ziyod
   Agar boĘ»lmasang iymon uchun OĘ»zing qoyam!
   Bor kuchim ila tirishsam ila ketar zoyam!

[V2]
 Bu dunyoning tashvishlari yoĘ»lim toĘ»sar
 Lekin iymonim kaloming ila bagĘ»rim oĘ»sar
 Qoldirmaysan bu hayotda meni oĘ»zing
 YoĘ»l ochadi bu yovlardan faqat soĘ»zing!</lyrics>
<title>Hayot yoĘ»li va soĘ»zlaring</title>
</song>